{"tid":1575501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好怪黨鐵，黨鐵出軌係為左唔跪低！","createTime":"2019-09-17T01:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T23:38:48.000Z","uid":42884,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"70950416b98157d3264aab82038d0c057758c488","tid":1575501,"uid":42884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:25:21.000Z","msg":"央視叫港鐵唔好脫軌，港鐵就偏要脫<br />\n簡直用心良苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n央視主持人警告出軌之後勿脫軌<br />\n<br />\n而在昨晚央視新聞聯播之後的「主播說聯播」節目中，主持人歐陽夏丹警告稱，「港鐵，你『出軌』了，下一步該怎麼走，可得要三思啊！因為弄不好，脫軌滑向深淵，也不是沒有可能！」<br />\n<br />\n對於官媒接連發聲批評，港鐵發出新聞稿解釋，當晚的做法是考慮到車站內有其他乘客滯留，於是安排空車接載乘客離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2434219/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E8%A9%95%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E7%AB%99%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%20%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%8B%BF%E5%87%BA%E8%BB%8C%E3%80%8C%E6%BB%91%E5%90%91%E6%B7%B1%E6%B7%B5%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%88%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87%EF%BC%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2434219%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E7%25AB%2599%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%2520%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%258B%25BF%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25BB%258C%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25BB%2591%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B7%25B5%25E3%2580%258D%25EF%25BC%2588%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2589%2587%25EF%25BC%2589&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rftobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=022d4600\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2434219/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E8%A9%95%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E7%AB%99%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%20%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%8B%BF%E5%87%BA%E8%BB%8C%E3%80%8C%E6%BB%91%E5%90%91%E6%B7%B1%E6%B7%B5%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%88%E6%9C%89%E7%8